Product Description

Micro HDMI to HDMI Cable

UGREEN Micro HDMI to HDMI cable supports 4K@60Hz, 2K@165HZ Full HD resolution, delivers high-definition video with 3D Technology, 18Gbps transmission speed and Audio Return Channel offers with uncompressed multichannel digital audio. It supports Micro HDMI to HDMI & HDMI to Micro HDMI, offers an ideal way to connect digital devices with Micro HDMI (HDMI D) ports to HDTVs or Projectors with full-size HDMI (HDMI A) ports.

Suitable for:

Mobile telephones / Smartphones / Tablet-PCs / HD-Camcorder / Digital cameras / Media-Center / HDTV devices / Projector / Plasma/TFT-TV / Monitors / DVR / Blu-ray-Player / Home Theatre Systems and more.

Notes

-HDMI ports supporting Ethernet are needed for internet sharing.

-This is not Micro USB, Does not work with Samsung Galaxy S3/S4/S5 or Samsung Tablets with Micro USB Connection.

Package Contents

UGREEN Micro HDMI (Type D) to HDMI (Type A) Cable x 1

Read more

Bi-Directional

Micro HDMI to HDMI cable offers an ideal way to connect digital devices with Micro HDMI (HDMI D) ports to HDTVs or Projectors with full-size HDMI (HDMI A) ports, delivers both high-definition video and digital audio from digital devices to your home theater.

Nyloin Braided

Tangle-free nylon braided material and wear-resistant aluminum shell make this Micro HDMI to HDMI adapter bend over 10000 bending, ensures secure fits & easy cable handling, much more durable for long-time performance.

Micro HDMI to HDMI

The Micro HDMI Adapter supports Micro HDMI to HDMI & HDMI to Micro HDMI, please kindly note this is NOT Micro USB or Mini HDMI, please confirm the device's port before purchasing

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.
